OL,3,CFake cancer charity worker stole
OL,4,C#18,000 from vulnerable men
OL,6,FA fraudster who pretended to be
OL,7,Fworking for a cancer charity has been
OL,8,Fjailed after taking over #18,000 from
OL,9,Ftwo vulnerable men.
OL,11,FWilliam Redmond tried to escape from
OL,12,Fpolice, who were alerted to a
OL,13,Fpotential fraud in a bank, but he was
OL,14,Fstopped by a member of the public
OL,15,Fbefore being arrested.
OL,17,FLiverpool Crown Court heard Redmond
OL,18,Fmade one victim take more than #10,000
OL,19,Ffrom cash machines over a year, while
OL,20,Fan elderly man was told to withdraw a
OL,21,Ftotal of #8,000 from his bank account.
