OL,6,FDetectives described his actions as
OL,7,F"truly unacceptable."
OL,9,FRedmond was recalled to prison for an
OL,10,Foutstanding sentence after his arrest
OL,11,Fin the bank in September 2023.
OL,13,FMerseyside Police discovered he had
OL,14,Fbeen defrauding a vulnerable man over
OL,15,Fa period of a year before the bank
OL,16,Fbecame aware of the fraud.
