OL,3,CFake cancer charity worker stole
OL,4,C#18,000 from vulnerable men
OL,6,FThe 33-year-old, from Walton Breck
OL,7,FRoad, Liverpool, had originally told
OL,8,Fthe victim that he was working for
OL,9,Fcancer charity Marie Curie, and then
OL,10,Ffabricated other reasons why he needed
OL,11,Fmore money.
OL,13,FThe victim, who said he felt pressured
OL,14,Fand intimidated, was visited by the
OL,15,Ffraudster several times a day, and
OL,16,Foften during the night where he was
OL,17,Fmade to attend cash points where he
OL,18,Fwithdrew more than #10,000.
